onsarten sowie Materialien.Und nicht zuletzt lädt ein Beispielteil mit besonders ansprechenden realisierten Projekten ein, sich für die eigene Praxis inspirieren zu lassen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aARCHITECTURE / Buildings / General.2bisacsh1 aPeter, Christine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aReisch, Daniel, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTemme, Katinka, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDETAIL eBook Package English 2001-2018z978311066216008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDETAIL eBook Package English 2001-2021z978311068956308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2018z9783110602999oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2018 Englishz978311060397208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978395553397740uhttps://doi.org/10.11129/978395553398440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783955533984423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783955533984.jpg  a978-3-11-060397-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-066216-0  DETAIL eBook Package English 2001-2018c2001d2018  a978-3-11-068956-3  DETAIL eBook Package English 2001-2021c2001d2021  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DADb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017